1
00:01:07,960 --> 00:01:08,800
What are you doing?

2
00:01:16,840 --> 00:01:17,720
Don't blame me.

3
00:01:18,640 --> 00:01:20,840
If your sworn brother hadn't led Dali Temple...

4
00:01:20,960 --> 00:01:22,120
...and driven me to a dead end...

5
00:01:22,680 --> 00:01:23,920
...I wouldn't treat you like this.

6
00:01:24,920 --> 00:01:26,840
I thought you only looked fierce...

7
00:01:27,920 --> 00:01:28,920
...but were kind at heart.

8
00:01:30,240 --> 00:01:31,640
Who knew you would actually commit...

9
00:01:31,640 --> 00:01:33,240
...such an act that outrages gods and men.

10
00:01:33,480 --> 00:01:34,680
I had no choice.

11
00:01:37,880 --> 00:01:38,600
You told me...

12
00:01:39,200 --> 00:01:40,880
...your dad was executed by the Imperial Court.

13
00:01:41,200 --> 00:01:42,680
You owe your life to your sworn brother.

14
00:01:42,880 --> 00:01:44,040
If he were not long for this world...

15
00:01:44,520 --> 00:01:45,400
...would you save him?

16
00:01:46,080 --> 00:01:47,480
Would you save him at any cost?

17
00:01:50,240 --> 00:01:50,520
I...

18
00:01:51,600 --> 00:01:52,480
I would.

19
00:01:54,280 --> 00:01:56,200
I owe my life to my Master.

20
00:01:57,520 --> 00:01:59,360
I don't care about the outrage of gods and men.

21
00:02:00,680 --> 00:02:02,680
I only seek my own peace of mind.

22
00:02:08,960 --> 00:02:11,640
This... is the knife wound I got...

23
00:02:11,960 --> 00:02:12,800
...when I fled last night.

24
00:02:15,120 --> 00:02:17,360
When and where were you injured last night?

25
00:02:19,320 --> 00:02:22,520
Hai Hour, not far from Wanhua Fang.

26
00:02:24,200 --> 00:02:24,880
Then why...

27
00:02:25,800 --> 00:02:27,640
...did you tear off the deceased's face?

28
00:02:29,120 --> 00:02:30,920
It was to prevent the authorities...

29
00:02:31,360 --> 00:02:32,600
...from identifying the deceased.

30
00:02:32,960 --> 00:02:34,000
So there would be nowhere to investigate.

31
00:02:37,600 --> 00:02:39,320
Very well. Then please...

32
00:02:41,920 --> 00:02:45,400
...draw the image you carved on the deceased.

33
00:02:48,720 --> 00:02:50,120
Since you can carve on flesh...

34
00:02:50,680 --> 00:02:52,480
...it must be effortless on paper.

35
00:02:53,400 --> 00:02:54,400
If you can truly draw it...

36
00:02:54,840 --> 00:02:56,080
...Dali Temple will convict you...

37
00:02:56,680 --> 00:02:58,160
...and spare the one you are determined to shield.

38
00:03:08,760 --> 00:03:09,040
Tong'er

39
00:03:12,840 --> 00:03:13,200
Tong'er

40
00:03:14,800 --> 00:03:15,120
This...

41
00:03:18,440 --> 00:03:19,400
They found you

42
00:03:21,320 --> 00:03:21,640
You...

43
00:03:28,520 --> 00:03:28,840
Master

44
00:03:30,360 --> 00:03:30,600
Master

45
00:03:34,760 --> 00:03:35,720
Why are you doing this?

46
00:03:36,400 --> 00:03:36,920
Tong'er

47
00:03:38,280 --> 00:03:40,040
My days are numbered anyway

48
00:03:40,720 --> 00:03:42,480
Let them catch me if they will

49
00:03:43,120 --> 00:03:43,680
Tell me

50
00:03:45,200 --> 00:03:47,480
Where did you go tonight?

51
00:03:48,600 --> 00:03:50,320
What did you do to them?

52
00:03:50,720 --> 00:03:52,560
You must tell me everything in detail

53
00:04:00,400 --> 00:04:02,120
I went to Wanhua Fang tonight

54
00:04:04,160 --> 00:04:04,760
At the Hour of Hai

55
00:04:09,000 --> 00:04:10,040
I killed them

56
00:04:10,800 --> 00:04:12,280
I took their livers

57
00:04:13,520 --> 00:04:15,000
I slashed their faces

58
00:04:17,440 --> 00:04:18,200
What else?

59
00:04:19,880 --> 00:04:20,320
That's all

60
00:04:24,360 --> 00:04:28,080
This child... he deceived me in the end

61
00:04:28,520 --> 00:04:29,080
Craftsman

62
00:04:29,600 --> 00:04:31,040
Do you know of a dark art in the underworld

63
00:04:31,840 --> 00:04:32,880
Called Wooden Puppet Life-Borrowing?

64
00:04:36,600 --> 00:04:38,280
As expected of someone from Dali Temple

65
00:04:39,440 --> 00:04:40,840
This room is full of the smell of medicinal plaster

66
00:04:41,480 --> 00:04:43,440
I presume the terminally ill person he wants to save

67
00:04:45,920 --> 00:04:46,640
Is you, right?

68
00:04:50,720 --> 00:04:51,200
That's right

69
00:04:52,600 --> 00:04:53,240
It is me

70
00:04:57,160 --> 00:04:58,880
Do you really believe in that life-borrowing dark art?

71
00:05:02,400 --> 00:05:02,960
At first

72
00:05:03,760 --> 00:05:05,600
Tong'er wanted to kill people to save my life

73
00:05:06,200 --> 00:05:07,200
I tried to stop him

74
00:05:08,640 --> 00:05:09,320
But people...

75
00:05:10,560 --> 00:05:11,800
The closer they get to death

76
00:05:12,440 --> 00:05:13,600
The more easily they succumb to fear

77
00:05:14,160 --> 00:05:15,280
The more fear is in the heart

78
00:05:15,440 --> 00:05:17,120
The... the harder it is to accept

79
00:05:17,840 --> 00:05:20,520
Why I am such a short-lived person

80
00:05:21,920 --> 00:05:24,760
Why Heaven is so unfair to me

81
00:05:30,320 --> 00:05:31,200
The more fearful one is

82
00:05:32,280 --> 00:05:33,520
The harder it is to let go

83
00:05:34,480 --> 00:05:37,840
The more reluctant the heart becomes

84
00:05:39,560 --> 00:05:41,480
Later, I stopped trying to hold him back

85
00:05:42,280 --> 00:05:44,160
I said... let him be

86
00:05:45,280 --> 00:05:45,720
It's all my fault

87
00:05:46,360 --> 00:05:47,400
It's all because of my greed

88
00:05:48,320 --> 00:05:49,400
I wanted to try again

89
00:05:50,520 --> 00:05:51,480
Extremely foolish

90
00:05:57,400 --> 00:05:58,360
Where is he now?

91
00:06:03,200 --> 00:06:05,040
The woman who gave birth to me

92
00:06:05,960 --> 00:06:07,160
Was a prostitute

93
00:06:08,120 --> 00:06:09,680
Since childhood, I was despised by everyone

94
00:06:11,440 --> 00:06:12,400
They cursed me

95
00:06:13,560 --> 00:06:14,040
Beat me

96
00:06:15,280 --> 00:06:18,720
Pointed at my nose and called me a prostitute's son

97
00:06:20,000 --> 00:06:20,600
As if

98
00:06:21,320 --> 00:06:22,400
I was born to be

99
00:06:22,400 --> 00:06:24,120
Like a puppet for people to smash

100
00:06:30,200 --> 00:06:32,720
In my anger, I destroyed my own face

101
00:06:33,920 --> 00:06:35,480
I wanted them to fear me

102
00:06:37,760 --> 00:06:38,480
But who knew

103
00:06:39,840 --> 00:06:41,160
Not only were they not afraid of me

104
00:06:42,560 --> 00:06:44,080
I became a monster

105
00:06:45,240 --> 00:06:45,800
An evil thing

106
00:06:53,640 --> 00:06:54,400
Xi Rou

107
00:06:57,480 --> 00:06:58,440
Besides Master

108
00:07:01,360 --> 00:07:03,280
Only you are willing to look at me directly

109
00:07:13,560 --> 00:07:14,200
You're not hurt, are you?

110
00:07:22,440 --> 00:07:23,960
Get away, you ugly freak!

111
00:07:24,120 --> 00:07:25,200
You scared my child!

112
00:07:27,400 --> 00:07:28,000
Ma'am, please.

113
00:07:28,440 --> 00:07:29,240
You shouldn't say that.

114
00:07:29,800 --> 00:07:30,360
This young man...

115
00:07:30,640 --> 00:07:31,640
...he only meant well.

116
00:07:32,160 --> 00:07:32,760
Meant well?

117
00:07:33,040 --> 00:07:33,600
What good could he mean?

118
00:07:34,240 --> 00:07:34,880
Look at that ugly face!

119
00:07:35,160 --> 00:07:36,480
He'll scare the life out of my child.

120
00:07:42,200 --> 00:07:42,880
Young man.

121
00:07:43,560 --> 00:07:44,280
What is your name?

122
00:07:45,880 --> 00:07:46,560
My name is Xi Rou.

123
00:07:47,040 --> 00:07:48,520
My home is not far ahead.

124
00:07:48,960 --> 00:07:50,720
Come have some tea when you're free.

125
00:07:54,800 --> 00:07:56,840
From the first moment I saw you...

126
00:07:58,160 --> 00:07:58,800
...I wanted...

127
00:07:59,760 --> 00:08:01,920
...to give all the remaining goodness in my heart...

128
00:08:02,640 --> 00:08:03,680
...to you.

129
00:08:05,480 --> 00:08:06,960
But fate is cruel.

130
00:08:12,800 --> 00:08:14,320
Once I save Master's life...

131
00:08:15,440 --> 00:08:16,240
...I will die too.

132
00:08:18,640 --> 00:08:20,240
I will use this worthless life of mine...

133
00:08:22,240 --> 00:08:22,840
...to repay you.

134
00:08:24,640 --> 00:08:25,360
Stop this!

135
00:08:26,720 --> 00:08:28,720
Turn back, Brother Liu Tong.

136
00:08:29,840 --> 00:08:30,880
Don't be so stubborn.

137
00:08:32,120 --> 00:08:33,280
Don't make any more mistakes.

138
00:08:35,480 --> 00:08:37,560
From the moment heaven gave me this worthless life...

139
00:08:39,520 --> 00:08:41,080
...all of this was destined.

140
00:09:00,000 --> 00:09:01,240
I won't let you feel any pain.

141
00:09:26,320 --> 00:09:27,240
My dirty hands...

142
00:09:29,080 --> 00:09:29,440
...are not worthy.

143
00:09:31,480 --> 00:09:31,960
Stop!

144
00:09:33,400 --> 00:09:33,800
Tong'er!

145
00:09:34,320 --> 00:09:34,600
Xi Rou!

146
00:09:36,240 --> 00:09:37,640
Liu Tong, let her go!

147
00:09:38,840 --> 00:09:39,120
Master.

148
00:09:39,800 --> 00:09:41,160
Tong'er can extend your life right now.

149
00:09:43,160 --> 00:09:46,120
Tong'er, Life-Borrowing is an evil art of the underworld.

150
00:09:46,560 --> 00:09:47,720
It is a delusion.

151
00:09:49,840 --> 00:09:51,720
I didn't stop you before...

152
00:09:52,240 --> 00:09:53,320
...and that was my mistake.

153
00:09:53,760 --> 00:09:55,080
Listen to me now.

154
00:09:55,840 --> 00:09:56,280
Let go.

155
00:09:56,800 --> 00:09:57,800
Let go!

156
00:09:58,120 --> 00:09:59,000
It is not a delusion!

157
00:10:00,680 --> 00:10:01,080
Master...

158
00:10:02,000 --> 00:10:02,480
I can save you.

159
00:10:03,360 --> 00:10:04,280
I know I can save you.

160
00:10:06,800 --> 00:10:08,200
The Five Viscera are only missing one now.

161
00:10:09,160 --> 00:10:09,960
I'll use my own!

162
00:10:10,720 --> 00:10:12,080
I can definitely save you!

163
00:10:12,400 --> 00:10:12,520
Stop!

164
00:10:12,600 --> 00:10:12,760
Tong'er!

165
00:10:19,360 --> 00:10:20,120
Master!

166
00:10:23,840 --> 00:10:24,440
Tong'er...

167
00:10:26,280 --> 00:10:29,880
Look at me now.

168
00:10:31,040 --> 00:10:32,960
Is this worth continuing your mistakes for?

169
00:10:34,480 --> 00:10:35,520
I was wrong.

170
00:10:36,840 --> 00:10:38,640
I was afraid of death and clung to life.

171
00:10:39,640 --> 00:10:42,320
I forced you down a path of no return.

172
00:10:43,400 --> 00:10:44,760
My selfishness...

173
00:10:45,840 --> 00:10:47,360
...has ruined my only...

174
00:10:49,680 --> 00:10:51,200
...my only apprentice.

175
00:10:52,320 --> 00:10:52,960
Master...

176
00:10:55,160 --> 00:10:55,560
Child...

177
00:10:57,160 --> 00:10:58,240
Let it go.

178
00:10:59,800 --> 00:11:00,840
You are still young.

179
00:11:01,720 --> 00:11:03,760
Don't burden yourself with so much sin.

180
00:11:05,080 --> 00:11:05,800
Master...

181
00:11:07,640 --> 00:11:08,720
Please...

182
00:11:34,200 --> 00:11:35,000
I believe that in your heart...

183
00:11:35,720 --> 00:11:36,680
...there is still goodness left.

184
00:11:37,800 --> 00:11:39,440
Otherwise, you wouldn't have kept that painting of the mother and child.

185
00:11:40,400 --> 00:11:41,240
I understand...

186
00:11:41,880 --> 00:11:42,560
...what is in your heart.

187
00:11:46,000 --> 00:11:47,960
Don't mention that Witch to me ever again!

188
00:11:51,320 --> 00:11:52,560
In this life...

189
00:11:54,480 --> 00:11:55,760
...I only have Master.

190
00:11:57,400 --> 00:11:57,720
Liu Tong!

191
00:12:15,960 --> 00:12:16,200
Guiyi

192
00:12:17,120 --> 00:12:17,640
Order Dali Temple

193
00:12:18,240 --> 00:12:19,040
to find Liu Tong's birth mother

194
00:12:20,880 --> 00:12:21,560
and bring him home.

195
00:12:27,800 --> 00:12:28,600
Come have some candy.

196
00:12:28,600 --> 00:12:30,240
I want some! I want some!

197
00:12:30,240 --> 00:12:31,600
Me too! Me too!

198
00:12:31,600 --> 00:12:31,640
Me too! Me too!

199
00:12:31,800 --> 00:12:32,520
Give me one!

200
00:12:32,600 --> 00:12:33,600
Me too! Me too!

201
00:12:34,040 --> 00:12:35,040
Don't push. There's enough for everyone.

202
00:12:35,160 --> 00:12:36,120
One at a time.

203
00:12:36,440 --> 00:12:37,080
Me too! Me too!

204
00:12:37,640 --> 00:12:38,840
I didn't expect my Vice Minister,

205
00:12:39,080 --> 00:12:40,600
usually so composed and steady,

206
00:12:41,080 --> 00:12:42,440
to have such a hideaway to relax.

207
00:12:42,600 --> 00:12:43,200
Share them among yourselves.

208
00:12:48,960 --> 00:12:50,640
These children have no parents.

209
00:12:51,440 --> 00:12:52,200
If no one looks after them,

210
00:12:53,120 --> 00:12:55,080
how many would end up like Liu Tong?

211
00:12:56,880 --> 00:12:58,280
You really are different from those in court

212
00:12:58,480 --> 00:13:00,200
who only care about power and profit.

213
00:13:01,680 --> 00:13:02,840
I'm starting to admire you a little.

214
00:13:04,720 --> 00:13:05,560
Since you put it that way,

215
00:13:06,080 --> 00:13:08,640
help me take care of them from now on.

216
00:13:12,200 --> 00:13:13,080
My Lord, Master.

217
00:13:14,680 --> 00:13:15,600
Liu Tong's mother has been found.

218
00:13:15,960 --> 00:13:16,960
Because Liu Tong went missing back then,

219
00:13:17,200 --> 00:13:19,080
his mother went mad searching for him.

220
00:13:24,840 --> 00:13:26,320
Hey, where is Xi Rou?

221
00:13:33,480 --> 00:13:35,880
Guiyi, bury Liu Tong.

222
00:13:42,640 --> 00:13:43,760
As a law enforcer,

223
00:13:44,520 --> 00:13:45,840
yet able to balance law and compassion.

224
00:13:46,840 --> 00:13:48,920
Your Lord is quite decent.
